{"word":"G5005 - ταλαίπωρος - talaípōros - tal-ah'-ee-po-ros - Wretched","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ταλαίπωρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">talaípōros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tal-ah'-ee-po-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wretched</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நிர்பந்தமான, நிர்பாக்கியமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"enduring toils and troubles, afflicted, wretched"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G5007 - τάλαντον - tálanton - tal'-an-ton/5007\">G5007</a> and a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G3984 - πεῖρα - peîra - pi'-rah/3984\">G3984</a>; <i>enduring trial</i>, that is, <i>miserable:</i> - wretched.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}